-height:150%;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">3.6</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n11.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">万㎡，其中车库面积</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">2.4</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n11.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">万㎡，设置</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">600</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n11.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">个停车位；急诊北侧</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">1-7</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n11.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">层接建，单层约</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">350</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n11.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">㎡；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">4</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n11.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">号楼东侧接建、新建连廊，占地面积约</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">2000</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n11.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">㎡（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">2-3</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n11.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">层）。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:1.5;layout-grid-mode:char;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\ncolor:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">4</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">、招标范围：盐城市老年康复医院改造建设工程勘察服务项目，服务内容包括</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\ncolor:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">(</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">但不限于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;color:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">)</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">按双方合同的约定在规定时间内完成建设单位委托项目的勘察服务</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\ncolor:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">(</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">收集已有资料、现场踏勘、制订勘察纲要，进行勘探、取样、试验、测试、检测、监测等勘察作业，以及编制工程勘察文件和岩土工程设计文件等</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\ncolor:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">)</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">，同时须取得行业管理部门的审查批准手续。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;color:black;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:1.5;layout-grid-mode:char;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\ncolor:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">5</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">、服务时间：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;color:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">7</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">个日历天内出具地质勘察成果文件</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;color:black;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">(</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n11.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">包括满足设计和施工要求的地质钻探、测量、试验等报告</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\ncolor:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">)</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">，具体服从招标人的安排。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;color:black;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:1.5;layout-grid-mode:char;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\ncolor:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">6</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">、质量要求：符合现行国家工程勘察技术规范、标准、规程，确保通过施工图审查机构审查。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\ncolor:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:1.5;layout-grid-mode:char;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">二、投标人须具备以下条件：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;color:black;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:1.5;layout-grid-mode:char;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\ncolor:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">、投标人资格要求：投标申请人须具有建设行政主管部门颁发的工程勘察综合资质或工程勘察专业资质</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\ncolor:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">(</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">岩土工程</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;color:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">)</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">勘察甲级资质的独立法人。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;color:black;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:1.5;layout-grid-mode:char;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\ncolor:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">2</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">、项目负责人为投标人本单位正式职工，具备国家注册土木工程师</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;color:black;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">(</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n11.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">岩土</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\ncolor:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">)</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">执业资格。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;color:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:1.5;layout-grid-mode:char;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\ncolor:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">3</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">、投标人须确保授权委托人和项目负责人为本单位的正式职工，并确保从投标截止日当月向前连续</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\ncolor:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">6</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">个月均在本单位缴纳养老保险</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;color:black;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">(</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">例：如开标日期为</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\ncolor:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">2021</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;color:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">11</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;color:black;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">**</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">日，则投标单位需保证以上人员</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\ncolor:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">2021</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;color:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">5</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">月—</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;color:black;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">10</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">月养老保险均在本单位缴纳。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\ncolor:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:1.5;layout-grid-mode:char;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\ncolor:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">4</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">、财务要求：投标人应具有独立订立合同的能力，未处于财产被接管、冻结和破产状态。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\ncolor:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style