yle=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">万㎡，其中车库面积</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;color:black\">2.4</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">万㎡，设置</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;color:black\">600</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">个停车位，新建投资约</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;color:black\">2.36</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">亿元。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\',\\\'serif\\\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:1.5;layout-grid-mode:\r\nchar;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5;color:black\">4</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">、招标范围：盐城市老年康复医院综合楼项目环境影响评估报告编制服务，以《盐城市老年康复医院综合楼项目》为研究对象，开展规划环境影响评价工作，编制规划环境影响报告书，成果符合相应的生态环境主管部门的审查技术要求，通过生态环境主管部门审查，具体内容详见任务书。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\',\\\'serif\\\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:1.5;layout-grid-mode:\r\nchar;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5;color:black\">5</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">、服务期要求：</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;color:black\"> 45 </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">日历天内完成，具体服务时间以招标人通知为准。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\',\\\'serif\\\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:1.5;layout-grid-mode:\r\nchar;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5;color:black\">6</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">、质量要求：满足国家及行业相关法律法规、标准规范要求，并确保通过招标人及相关行业主管部门技术的审核，并获得相应的批复。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\',\\\'serif\\\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:1.5;layout-grid-mode:\r\nchar;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">三、投标人须具备以下条件：</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\',\\\'serif\\\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:1.5;layout-grid-mode:\r\nchar;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5;color:black\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">、投标人资格要求：投标人须是在中国境内注册，具有能力完成本次招标内容的独立法人。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\',\\\'serif\\\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:1.5;layout-grid-mode:\r\nchar;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5;color:black\">2</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">、项目负责人为投标人本单位正式职工，须具有环境影响评价工程师职业资格证书。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\',\\\'serif\\\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:1.5;layout-grid-mode:\r\nchar;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5;color:black\">3</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">、投标人须确保授权委托人和项目负责人为本单位的正式职工，并确保从投标截止日当月向前连续</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;color:black\">6</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">个月均在本单位缴纳养老保险</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;color:black\">(</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">例：如开标日期为</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;color:black\">2021</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">年</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;color:black\">11</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">月</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;color:black\">**</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">日，则投标单位需保证以上人员</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;color:black\">2021</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">年</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;color:black\">5</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">月—</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;color:black\">10</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">月养老保险均在本单位缴纳。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\',\\\'serif\\\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:1.5;layout-grid-mode:\r\nchar;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5;color:black\">4</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">、财务要求：投标人应具有独立订立合同的能力，未处于财产被接管、冻结和破产状态。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\',\\\'serif\\\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:1.5;layout-grid-mode:\r\nchar;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5;color:black\">5</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">、本次招标不接受联合体投标。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\',\\\'serif\\\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:1.5;layout-grid-mode:\r\nchar;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">四、投标保证金</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;color:black\">:</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">本项目投标保证金数额为人民币</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;color:black\">2000</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">元整，具体详见招标文件。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\',\\\'serif\\\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:1.5;layout-grid-mode:\r\nchar;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">五、评标办法</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;color:black\">:</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">本项目采用“竞争性谈判”法，具体详见招标文件。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\',\\\'serif\\\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:1.5;layout-grid-mode:\r\nchar;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">六、招标文件领取：</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\',\\\'serif\\\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:1.5;layout-grid-mode:\r\nchar;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">投标报名及竞争性谈判文件的获取，请符合上述资质条件的投标人携带单位介绍信</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;color:black\">(</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">或授权委托书，须注明联系人、电话及邮箱</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;color:black\">)</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">原件到</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">江苏全盛工程造价事务所有限公司</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;color:black\">(</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">盐城市解放南路</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;color:black\">199</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">号阳光大厦</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;color:black\">B</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">座四楼</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;color:black\">)</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">投标报名，投标报名时间</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;color:black\">2021</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">年</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;color:black\">12</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">月</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;color:black\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">日</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;color:black\">8</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">时</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;color:black\">30</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">分至</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;color:black\">2021</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">年</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;color:black\">12</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">月</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;color:black\">6</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">日</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;color:black\">18</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">时。联系人：</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">祁建峰</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">；手机：</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;color:black\">13626206678</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\',\\\'serif\\\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:1.5;layout-grid-mode:\r\nchar;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">七、本项目严禁挂靠，一经核实挂靠，将被取消投标、中标资格，并按相关规定进行处罚，直至建议有关部门吊销资质证书。</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;color:black\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\\\'Times New Roman\\\',\\\'serif\\\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:1.5;layout-grid-mode:\r\nchar;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">八、投标申请人有违反《盐城市市场廉政准则规定</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;color:black\">(</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">试行</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;color:black\">)</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:bl