2.0pt;font-family:宋体\">1.1</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">项目名称：盐城市第一人民医院主院区<span>ICU</span>、<span>CCU</span>氧气管道改造工程项目。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\\\'Calibri\\\',\\\'sans-serif\\\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\\\'Calibri\\\',\\\'sans-serif\\\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:24.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">1.2</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">项目地点：盐城市第一人民医院主院区（人民南路<span>66</span>号）</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\\\'Calibri\\\',\\\'sans-serif\\\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\\\'Calibri\\\',\\\'sans-serif\\\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:24.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">1.3</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">招标内容：盐城市第一人民医院主院区<span>ICU</span>、<span>CCU</span>氧气管道改造工程。具体内容详见招标人提供的图纸及工程量清单。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\\\'Calibri\\\',\\\'sans-serif\\\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\\\'Calibri\\\',\\\'sans-serif\\\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:24.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">1.4</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">工期要求：<u><span> 30 </span></u>日历天，具体开工日期以招标人的书面通知为准；</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\\\'Calibri\\\',\\\'sans-serif\\\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\\\'Calibri\\\',\\\'sans-serif\\\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:24.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">1.5</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">发包方式：包工包料。<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\\\'Calibri\\\',\\\'sans-serif\\\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\\\'Calibri\\\',\\\'sans-serif\\\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:24.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">1.6</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">质量要求：</span><span style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">符合国家“合格”标准，质保期<span>2</span>年。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\\\'Calibri\\\',\\\'sans-serif\\\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\\\'Calibri\\\',\\\'sans-serif\\\';margin-left:0cm;text-indent:24.1pt;line-height:24.0pt\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">2、</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">投标人应当具备的主要资格条件：</span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\\\'Calibri\\\',\\\'sans-serif\\\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\\\'Calibri\\\',\\\'sans-serif\\\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:21.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">2.1</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">、投标人应具有建设行政主管部门核发的机电安装工程施工总承包三级及以上资质或建筑机电安装工程专业承包三级及以上资质的独立法人，并取得安全生产许可证。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\\\'Calibri\\\',\\\'sans-serif\\\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\\\'Calibri\\\',\\\'sans-serif\\\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:21.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">2.2</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">、投标人项目负责人必须是投标人本单位的正式职工，并具有机电安装工程专业的二级（含）以上建造师注册证书，同时具有安全生产考核合格证（<span>B</span>类）。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\\\'Calibri\\\',\\\'sans-serif\\\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\\\'Calibri\\\',\\\'sans-serif\\\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:21.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">2.4</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">、投标人应具有医疗器械生产许可证、医疗器械生产产品登记表。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\\\'Calibri\\\',\\\'sans-serif\\\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\\\'Calibri\\\',\\\'sans-serif\\\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:21.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">2.5</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">、投标人应具有医用中心供氧系统《医疗器械注册证》以及《医疗器械注册登记表》。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\\\'Calibri\\\',\\\'sans-serif\\\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\\\'Calibri\\\',\\\'sans-serif\\\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:21.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">2.6</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">、投标人应具有特种设备生产许可证<span> (</span>压力管道安装<span>)GC2</span>级。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\\\'Calibri\\\',\\\'sans-serif\\\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\\\'Calibri\\\',\\\'sans-serif\\\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:21.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">2.7</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">、本次招标不接受联合体投标。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\\\'Calibri\\\',\\\'sans-serif\\\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\\\'Calibri\\\',\\\'sans-serif\\\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:21.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">2.8</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">、财务要求：投标人应具有独立订立合同的能力，未处于财产被接管、冻结和破产状态。\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\\\'Calibri\\\',\\\'sans-serif\\\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\\\'Calibri\\\',\\\'sans-serif\\\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:21.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">2.9</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">、信誉要求：投标人没有被国家、江苏省省级有关部门及盐城市级有关部门暂停招投标或市场准入资格且在公示处罚期内。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\\\'Calibri\\\',\\\'sans-serif\\\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\\\'Calibri\\\',\\\'sans-serif\\\';text-align:left;text-indent:24.1pt;\r\nline-height:21.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char\" align=\"left\"><b><span style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">3</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n宋体\">、投标报名及招标文件的获取</span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\\\'Calibri\\\',\\\'sans-serif\\\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:24.0pt;\r\nbackground:white\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">请符合上述资质条件的投标人携带单位介绍信原件到江苏仁禾中衡工程咨询房地产估价有限公司造价二部（盐城市青年西路<span>8</span>号<span>8</span>楼<span>805</span>室）投标报名并领取招标文件，投标报名时间<span>2021</span>年<span>12</span>月<span>1</span>日<span>8</span>时<span>30</span>分至<span>2021</span>年<span>12</span>月<span>7</span>日<span>18</span>时。联系人：刘永杰，<span>0515-69057406</span>；手机：<span>13626222271</span>。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\\\'Calibri\\\',\\\'sans-serif\\\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:24.0pt;\r\nbackground:white\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">、</span><b><span style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体\">本项目评标办法采用“合理低价法”。</span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\\\'Calibri\\\',\\\'sans-serif\\\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:24.0pt;\r\nbackground:white\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">、投标申请人有违反《盐城市市场廉政准则规定（试行）》中规定情形的，招标人将拒绝投标报名。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\\\'Calibri\\\',\\\'sans-serif\\\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:24.0pt;\r\nbackground:white\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">、招投标监督管理机构及投诉电话：盐城市第一人民医院纪检监察室，联系电话<span>0515-66696810</span>。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\\\'Calibri\\\',\\\'sans-serif\\\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:24.0pt;\r\nbackground:white\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">其余内容详见招标文件。<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\\\'Calibri\\\',\\\'sans-serif\\\';text-align:right;background:white\" align=\"right\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">招标人：盐城市第一人民医院</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\\\'Calibri\\\',\\\'sans-serif\\\';text-align:right;background:white;word-break:break-all\" align=\"r