挥专业特长，耐心细致地为前来就诊的患者提供看诊服务，提出合理的治疗方案；结合实例及课件，就<span>“</span>房颤治疗<span>”“</span>造口旁疝的诊断和治疗<span>”“VTE</span>的规范预防<span>”“</span>两例肺栓塞患者的护理体验<span>”</span>等主题为大丰区三院的医护人员提供了专业的学术讲座。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:等线;text-indent:28.0pt;line-height:26.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:仿宋,仿宋_GB2312;color:black;background:white\">2019</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:仿宋,仿宋_GB2312;color:black;background:white\">年，为提高大丰区三院的整体医疗服务能力，更好地为大丰人民健康保驾护航，农工党市一院总支与大丰区三院签订了<span>“</span>战略合作<span>”</span>协议，通过两年多的活动已取得了一定的实效。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:等线;text-indent:28.0pt;line-height:26.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:仿宋,仿宋_GB2312;color:black;background:white\">邓义军主委指出，此次活动既是农工党市一院总支为战略合作单位大丰区三院提供的一次义诊服务，也是市一院总支积极响应市“十四五规划”，建立区域医疗联盟的重要活动。他表示，今后将进一步加强在大丰区三院的活动力度，根据大丰区三院的实际需求制定精确合作方案，积极为基层医疗建设发展添砖加瓦。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:等线;text-indent:28.0pt;line-height:26.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:仿宋,仿宋_GB2312;color:black;background:white\"><a href=\"/ewebeditor/uploadfile/image/2021/12/07/20211207093141673.jpg\" target=\"_blank\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;<img src=\"/ewebeditor/uploadfile/image/2021/12/07/20211207093141673_s.jpg\" border=\"0\"></a><br>\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:等线;text-indent:28.0pt;line-height:26.0pt\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;<a href=\"/ewebeditor/uploadfile/image/2021/12/07/20211207093958602.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"/ewebeditor/uploadfile/image/2021/12/07/20211207093958602_s.jpg\" border=\"0\"></a></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:等线;text-indent:28.0pt;line-height:26.0pt\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</p>\',\n  ),\n  \'author\' => \'\',\n  \'editer\' => \'\',\n  \'list_order\' => \'2021-12-07 09:40:15\',\n  \'views\' => 0,\n  \'verify\' => 1,\n  \'html\' => \'1\',\n  \'html_view_url_rule\' => \'\',\n  \'seo_keywords\' => \'\',\n  \'seo_description\' => \'\',\n  \'template\' => \'\',\n  \'config\' => \n  array (\n    \'allow_ip\' => \n    array (\n      \'enabled\' => \'0\',\n      \'collectip\' => \'\',\n      \'beginip\' => \'\',\n      \'endip\' => \'\',\n      \'ruleoutip\' => \'\',\n    ),\n  ),\n  \'custom_a\' => \'\',\n  \'model\' => \'article\',\n  \'verified\' => \'1\',\n  \'id\' => \'3152\',\n  \'iid\' => \'3152\',\n  \'page\' => \'1\',\n  \'_referer\' => \'http://192.168.162.72/admin.php/cms/item-list\',\n  \'credit_type\' => \'0\',\n  \'credit\' => \'1\',\n  \'action\' => \'update\',\n  \'attachment_hash\' => \'1cf83ecdd3942dd6\',\n  \'verifier\' => \'宣传处\',\n)','1638841299');
